ivardefs.name: milestone
ivardefs.desc: The milestones the subject has passed through.

ivardefs.name: reason
ivardefs.desc: The reason for the state change.  If coded it should follow the formal subject state model.

ivardefs.name: startDate
ivardefs.desc: The date when the change in status occurred.

ivardefs.name: state
ivardefs.desc: The current state of the subject.

ivardefs.name: type
ivardefs.desc: Identifies the aspect of the subject's journey that the state refers to.

properties.desc: The current state (status) of the subject and resons for status change where appropriate.
